a404 10
<blockquote>
  <table border="0" width="800">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#eeeeee" nowrap="nowrap"><b>Mac hmac-md5</b> </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</blockquote>
<h2><a name="2.4">2.4 - Mi&eacute;rt &iacute;rja ki az OpenSSH, hogy:
